                            <comment id="304037" author="yujian" created="Wed, 9 Jun 2021 17:56:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thank you, Robin.&lt;br/&gt;
The back-ported patch for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13182&quot; title=&quot;MAP_POPULATE hangs with Linux 5.4&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-13182&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-13182&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; on Lustre b2_12 branch is &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/43958&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/43958&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

