&lt;p&gt;Do you have any sense whether &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/43725/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/43725/&lt;/a&gt; is sufficient for a ZFS server?&lt;/p&gt;

